{
  "stem": "7414.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So once, I am walking in the street, and who stands at the tram stop?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The sister of my sister-in-law under false papers as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met from time to time, in-- in a church or somewhere, this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when-- after the story with the Gestapo, when I was released and I come home, back, I met her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told her the story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First of all, to warn her that it will not be very safe for us to meet again, you know, because this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To-- to tell her, I told her the story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she told me that her-- she was working as a housekeeper in a German household.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this woman, the-- this woman, or some other woman around, has a friend on the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she will try to ask, because I was dying to know what happens to my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She will try to get to know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the friend was just the Pole who was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he told her they either were shot on the spot in the cellars of the headquarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I know that she is Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But she impressed me so with her behavior that I helped her in the last moment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was his answer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remembered what the Schupo told me on the landing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you behave the same way, you are going to get out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, the tragedy is-- I-- first of all, I wrote straight to my husband, with whom I was still in contact.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was hidden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto was finished by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was hidden by a Polish family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I wrote there, and I wrote him as much as I could.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he understand what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
